parameters: Mage Leso: That crescent moon... Are you from the academy?
Mage Relm: Yes, is there a problem?

Mage Leso: I never expected that the mage of the Great Rock
Castle would seek help from the Magic Academy.
Mage Leso: Sigh... It's lamentable to be so powerless.

Priestess Sophia: Regarding Miss Anato, she was quite
fatigued.

Priestess Sophia: Is there a problem with what I'm wearing,
by any chance?

Mage Leso: Your thinking is correct. That outfit is a sacred
treasure passed down in our clan.

Mage Leso: It bestows great magical power upon the wearer,
but at the same time, it also brings powerful damage caused
by magic.
Thief Nora: Y-You need to take that off quickly!

Mage Leso: Mages are foolish creatures, seeking to observe
even their own destruction in the pursuit of research.

Mage Leso: I want you to stop her, she's my only daughter...
Please!

Clea: I came here on a request, and if it's a father's wish,
I can't ignore it.
Clea: Please leave it to us.

Mage Relm: It's fine to be excited, but we won't win unless
we solve the mystery of that nonsense magic power!

Mage Relm: It's not just my own magical power... I had a
sensation that I was gathering magic power from somewhere.

Mage Leso: I want you to go to the underground laboratory
and release the magic power of the crystal there. That
should do the trick.

Mage Relm: If you do that, the crystal won't be usable
anymore, you know?

Mage Leso: It's for the sake of my daughter, so feel free to
do as you please.
Mage Relm: Sigh... Fine, I understand. I'll do as I please!

Mage Leso: I can't believe Anat is just leaving all six
crystals untouched.
Mage Leso: Thank you for helping my daughter, Anato.

Mage Leso: Her physical exhaustion is severe, so she won't
be able to get up from the bed for a while.

Mage Leso: If you hadn't stopped her, I wonder what would
have happened to Anato... You are her benefactors.

Mage Relm: Well, her personality may be something, but her
magic is the real deal!

Mage Leso: I dislike the authoritarian ways of the Magic
Academy, but as an individual mage, I am grateful to you.
Mage Leso: If you don't mind, I would like you to take this.
Mage Relm: Isn't it the treasure of our clan!?
Mage Leso: It would be difficult for Anato to see that.

Mage Relm: Alright, if you insist on saying that much, then
this genius will take it!

Mage Leso: I will focus on Anato's treatment. If there's
anything, I'll request assistance on the Mucos bulletin
board.
Clea: Yes, leave it to me.

Mage Leso: I would be happy if Anato could become friends
with you once she recovers.
Mage Leso: I'm counting on you, Anato...
Mage Leso: Thank you for helping Anahto.
Clea (Let's do it after getting permission)

events.name: EV017創設者の行方　レソ

parameters: 2.演出開始　【100】創設者の行方　1-3　戦闘前
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Mage Leso: I've heard about dragons. It's an honor to meet a
real dragon slayer.
Clea: I have a favor to ask today.

Mage Leso: Information about negotiator Proposhi... Indeed,
he had a strong connection with the first guild master,
Prus.

Mage Leso: And in the library of the Great Rock Castle,
there are numerous documents left behind by negotiator
Proposhi.

Thief Nora: That's absolutely right! As expected of Mr.
Agonia, you're amazing!

Priestess Sophia: However, I can't teach you for free...
Hehe, you're making that kind of expression.

Mage Leso: You owe a great debt, but negotiator Proposhi is
of great value to our clan.
Mage Leso: As a condition for the exchange--

Mage Anat: I lost before due to my costume going out of
control, but this time I'll show you Anat's true power!

Mage Relm: I would be happy to show you once again who the
real genius is!

Mage Leso: I might be laughed at again for being a doting
parent, but I want you all to see how much my daughter has
grown--
Swift Celis: ...I win. Guide me to the library.
Swift Celis: Could it be that I made a mistake?

Clea: Yes, I don't think they're expecting something like
that.
Swift Celis: ...Sorry, can I stand up?
Mage Anat: Y-Yes, I'm fine. I'm not injured.

Mage Leso: Oh, well, I want you all to see how much my
daughter has grown, so please regain your focus.
Clea: Understood, I will proceed with the evaluation.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Mage Leso: Are you ready yet?
2.演出開始　【100】創設者の行方　1-3　戦闘
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Mage Relm: I've been curious, but do you have multiple
outfits?

Mage Anat: This is a replica! However, Anat has infused it
with magic power...

Mage Anat: This might become a future family heirloom, you
know!

Mage Anat: Hehe, I wonder if I went a little too far with my
seriousness?

Mage Leso: Sorry, but I can't give you any information. Feel
free to challenge as many times as you want and let me know.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Mage Leso: Are you ready yet?
2.演出開始　【100】創設者の行方　1-3　再戦
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Mage Anat: Hehe, I wonder if I went a little too serious?

Mage Leso: Sorry, but I can't give you any information. Feel
free to challenge as many times as you want and let me know
when you're ready.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
2.演出開始　【100】創設者の行方　1-3　勝利後
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Mage Relm: You put up a good fight against this genius,
hehe. How about a one-on-one next time?

Mage Anat: ...I still have room to grow, Anat! Just wait
until the genius becomes a super genius, and then a mega
super genius!

Mage Relm: I appreciate you fighting against me. That child
is certainly a genius, but they have a tendency to become
conceited.

Mage Relm (It's because you're too soft on Anat, no doubt
about it!)

Priestess Sophia (It feels like being an overprotective
parent to the extreme, doesn't it?)
Thief Nora (It's as sweet as honey...)
Clea: Isn't it a matter of Leso-san's education?

Mage Leso: Well, well, I have no words to retort... As
promised, I will guide you to the special library in the
Castle of Great Rocks.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Mage Leso: It seems like there was some progress. You don't
have to tell me, it's something important that you obtained.

Mage Leso: I'm personally curious too. I hope you can find
out what happened to Pruce safely.
